90920,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"兒登好耐無見過咁痴線既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b995df44cf8efb38add789286c7ccfc9797faa52","tid":690920,"uid":152759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T20:12:42.000Z","msg":"嘩 好撚癲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a4d27c010a12e57c0a3d40a351952d5f6a295f","tid":690920,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64f522f0b45510692024f052ff9de42093aba091","tid":690920,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:03:29.000Z","msg":"好想瘋狂咁賴金盈個大脾內側<br />\n條脷輕輕咁掃吓羅鈺文個西<br />\n<br />\n再好玩啲o既<br />\n可以考慮同梁凱寧扑嘢個陣<br />\n一定會叫佢一路報住天氣一路扑<br />\n如果佢唔小心興奮一叫<br />\n就會就一巴扯埋去<br />\n同佢講咪撚呻吟呀<br />\n專業啲呀讀稿機器<br />\n繼續讀稿呀<br />\n唔係一掌打撚爆你對波<br />\n<br />\n但講到尾<br />\n陳嘉欣呢啲撚屌先最有征服感<br />\n平時响講清講楚入面有撚晒立場<br />\n你要响床上面<br />\n大大聲同佢講而家邊個先係話事嗰個<br />\n我今次一定要親中你！<br />\n佢會好驚，問返你咩叫親中你。。。<br />\n你要一巴扯埋去<br />\n同佢講<br />\n親中咪親中囉，臭八婆！親自中出呀屌你老母！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T20:22:36.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣終於講返句人話了"},{"pid":"5f629a3f82985dab1bf243695968c366bcc7dfaf","tid":690920,"uid":10890,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T20:29:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n平時一大早起身見到新聞小珍報新聞<br />\n<br />\n我已經&quot;動L&quot;左既小弟弟就想向佢發炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但為求對小珍既尊重<br />\n<br />\n於是我特登谷左五日唔打飛機<br />\n<br />\n諗住一炮過射俾小珍，俾佢做facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經谷左五日如箭在弦既小弟弟再忍唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n一開電視，小珍已經係到ready 緊我d面部護理&quot;精&quot;華&quot;液&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用手將小弟弟好似shotgun咁狂chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎顏射佢既時候...你老母<br />\n<br />\n電視突然轉左做當奴曾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾億精兵又忍唔住出左一半，收唔撚番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是一路嗌：哎呀，仆街啦，你老母，呀...呀...呀...呀...呀...<br />\n<br />\n就咁我幾億子彈射左落當奴塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，而家仲好撚興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，早知下次定住個畫面先射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五日既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aee2610a254b42c497da61327ac89f0cf84a33d","tid":690920,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T20:32:08.000Z","msg":"good<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ba7ae0d9a85de6edc291d8d4d